Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.54,0:00:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊  已经慢我一圈了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.76,0:00:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么能输啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抓住咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.73,0:00:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.43,0:00:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎  这是那个时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.62,0:00:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大不了的  已经不碍事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们继续跑吧  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.91,0:00:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.70,0:00:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:23.98,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第3话\N黑和蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.55,0:02:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛将近  早上和午休都要练习
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了节省时间  午饭就在这里吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.66,0:02:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家把便当都带来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要为练习做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要比平常的多一些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜啊  一眼就看出在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这是所有人都要参加吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.01,0:02:49.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在午休就有些…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.18,0:02:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都  这是针对你的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要你这样的初学者直接去参加比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.47,0:02:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须在短时间内加强锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:03:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧  大家都会帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠也会对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.31,0:03:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么今天就到这  大家换衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来我们去订购护具
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:40.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馅料中使用北海道产红豆慢工制出的极品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:44.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再用吹弹可破般的糯米皮料包裹住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.52,0:03:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清爽的甜味中参杂着淡淡咸味搭配出绝妙的口感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  老师  你来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有新部员入部啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:03:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我看看竹剑和护具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请便请便
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  都这么久了你也让我再去指导一下部员的练习嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈…再说吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人是有段数的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我曾拜托他担任教练
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:18.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就进入状态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉就好像电视剧里面的热血教师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把大家练到都站不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后带着完成使命的男人的笑容离去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是…很棒的笑容啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但之后被部员臭骂的人是我啊！这谁受得了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我什么时候再去好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？这个…坂口先生也很忙吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很闲哦  很闲的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了闲再没别的了  真是遗憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且让强一些的人来指导对部员也比较好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  以前你怎么样我是不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在是没有在练习了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我每周都有去道场哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要取得好成绩的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要找我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  坂口先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…珠？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是这里的部员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你平日的指导
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.37,0:05:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代我向你爸爸问好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是竹剑  其他人也随便看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.99,0:05:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不都一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:38.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要买38了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三八是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉哟！这家伙是个糊涂鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在说竹剑的种类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长度是三尺八寸  所以简称38
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中的正式战中不用这个是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算长度差不多一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但重量就区别很大了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.11,0:05:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要自己掂量好了挑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然亲手挥一下来确认是最好的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的豆大福…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说话啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有木刀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护具…选哪个都无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子因为有胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微选大一点的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  你这是性骚扰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:06:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么！这不是事实吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要这个！好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那个很贵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要留下手印！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都  你看怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.29,0:07:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒哦  段郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  给你奖励
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  都说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在制服上套护具真白痴啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  段郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:29.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是都说了吗  那样吃的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:31.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  听我说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福我算是得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个大叔可是有些硬来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我还真要感谢你加入呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然家里还有道场  也很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是为了正义
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  因为我认为这样做是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我会认真对待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.21,0:07:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我会尽快送过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅了  那就拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆大福真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢皮更厚一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  马上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.95,0:08:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个月一定能比赛的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.55,0:08:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我要是赢了怎么办还没决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  看来我不做点什么也不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我们赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就要拿走装饰在你房间里的那样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装饰在我房间里的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.24,0:08:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最珍视的…那样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是Super Famicom吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:56.01,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,スーファミ：スーパーファミコン(Super Famicom)的简称，\N任天堂于1990年发行的游戏机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:56.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:08:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奖杯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.41,0:09:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那本来就是我的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赢了你就把它还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在也不能再互相对战了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交给我们的学生决定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没拿来装饰房间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是混在搬家的行李中带来了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛结束！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊  前辈  我侥幸打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运气真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  无论是侥幸还是运气  结果就是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你赢了  小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小次郎  我就要毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.62,0:10:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之前比一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈你不是都引退了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是因为不甘心输给这么侥幸的我对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就用奖杯作赌注…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是这回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这回事！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.84,0:10:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.06,0:10:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的奖杯你有好好收着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我赢了  你就给我奖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼神很认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那时候那么说  前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.41,0:11:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道中没有侥幸和运气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:21.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈  那时的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的要比你强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话这东西对我来说根本无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.78,0:11:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我不能输！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:52.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}练习目录！\N这是小都都的\N加油咯！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.89,0:11:57.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～真像部长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们剑道部也渐渐正式化了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小鞘发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她差不多也该回来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:17.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为最强的选手了  接下来是「哦！小都都」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:47.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧！我死了算了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞘子你吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:13:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是没有才能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧…小说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奔跑吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞘子！这么晚你上哪去！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要做到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:24.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做到！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是天才！是天才！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.21,0:13:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是日本第一！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是天才所以我办得到！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  她老是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做到！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次  荣花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,订购的竹剑送到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息的时候来部团教室…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:11.01,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（领队在视听教室）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就留言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次  这是不是纪梨乃前辈写的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:30.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}给勇次和其他人\N竹内\N来了哦\N纪梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:30.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}（竹内、因为发音和日文竹剑相同所以写成了这样的别字）]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.85,0:14:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:44.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（内有竹刀）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.49,0:14:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大中午就来练习  开什么玩笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:56.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:14:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真是太放不开了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再找个人来发泄一下不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个一年级的应该也已经不去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再去教训教训他？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等不急
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天去社团露个脸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:22.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  不揍个人我消不了气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防具送到了  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家各自去确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有就是尽快把钱交上来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是账单
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱可以交给老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我先保管着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先保管？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…你们这些不信任的眼光算什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  大家来试带护具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先保管？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.59,0:16:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会乱用啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会私吞的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.66,0:16:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个要怎么戴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣花  不能先戴头盔的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  首先系好腰垂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.71,0:16:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颈绳也要自己系好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴上手套就不能系了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像七五三
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:23.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（七五三是日本独特的节日，可以看作是儿童节一样的存在）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠你也买了新护具啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  你家不是开道场的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为大家都买了  所以我也想要新的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的护具已经很旧了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上第一次参加部团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和大家一起开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以觉得道具也一起换新比较好…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.76,0:17:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  你是红色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错！这是为了打倒前辈的队伍所聚集起来的正义战士们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而领队  红色就是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:12.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  那我这个部长呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄色！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.69,0:17:22.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给人的角色感觉就是黄色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么角色感觉啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.18,0:17:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  那么小都都呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然是粉红了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好像一瞬间看到黑色了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:42.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是蓝色的鞘子和还没找到的绿色！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要将五个人召集在我石田司令麾下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:52.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么一定会赢得胜利！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.27,0:17:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就那么在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.31,0:18:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是女生太不公平了  老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.66,0:18:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊？你果然还是黄色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不全都成黄色了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要啦  这样的战队
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  男生们就在暗中支持女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说蓝色还没有复活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.44,0:18:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她还在请假期间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  前段时间有发「我要死了」的短信来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  这不糟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:30.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.07,0:18:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心  常有的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  早晚会知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么一年级的  来戴上名布看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插到腰垂那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  粉红？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎的名布…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是「荣花」而变成「荣光」了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:57.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打击～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:19:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在店里写的字太丑  所以才搞错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.23,0:19:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎…我们再买新的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  而且这样更帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看啊！可以看到闪耀着无意义的金光哦！金光！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都  你要回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉哦  今天要打工
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？是今天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为突然被拜托…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得给大家说一声哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.04,0:19:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上我会给你打电话的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  段郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气  任性的女孩子也很可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀唉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:47.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…前段时间的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会经过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前虽然看到过几次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  安下心来慢慢等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.43,0:20:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要带小都都来哦  段
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是最需要练习的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我会跟她说的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴  这点根本不够
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系  你就忍忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:40.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你玩剑道根本没成长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.61,0:20:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是小鞘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管她的  我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起！有没有受伤？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为刹车失灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们学校的制服…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.33,0:21:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你！这样也太过分了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.36,0:21:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.44,0:21:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.75,0:23:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  我是小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.54,0:23:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我还是初学者  但是剑道真是很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.73,0:23:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问有什么有趣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.89,0:23:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以用棒子打人敲人揍人  而且还都是合法的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.97,0:24:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}viva violence{\r}\N暴力万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.83,0:24:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仅是身体
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.86,0:24:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神方面都能受到锻炼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.58,0:24:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想像一下对方痛苦的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.42,0:24:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心中的S心就蠢蠢欲动
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学习团队合作精神
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.18,0:24:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为人也得到成长了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.20,0:24:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且说回来只要我有了段郎就什么都可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.38,0:24:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  下回是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.75,0:24:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「粉红和蓝」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.70,0:24:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M的家伙一定要看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.07,0:24:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说记得给老娘看！
